          "orderIndex": 1,
          "label": "السؤال 1",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "المعادلة $2e^{2x}+3e^x-2=0$ ذات المجهول الحقيقي $x$: (أ) تقبل حلا وحيدا، (ب) تقبل حلين مختلفين، (ج) لا تقبل حلا."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q1_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (أ): للمعادلة حل وحيد هو $-\\ln 2$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q1_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s1_e2_q2",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s1_e2",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "السؤال 2",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$\\displaystyle\\int_0^1(3x^2+3e^{3x})\\,dx$ يساوي: (أ) $e^3+1$، (ب) $e^3$، (ج) $e^3-1$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q2_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (ب)، لأن $\\int_0^1(3x^2+3e^{3x})\\,dx=[x^3+e^{3x}]_0^1=e^3$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s1_e2_q3",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s1_e2",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "السؤال 3",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "المتتالية العددية المعرفة بـ $u_0=1$، ومن أجل كل عدد طبيعي $n$: $u_{n+1}=2u_n+1$ لها عبارة الحد العام: (أ) $2^{n+1}+1$، (ب) $2^n-1$، (ج) $2^{n+1}-1$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q3_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (ج): $u_n=2^{n+1}-1$، وهي الوحيدة التي تحقق $u_0=1$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q3_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s1_e2_q4",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s1_e2",
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "label": "السؤال 4",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q4_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$\\displaystyle\\lim_{x\\to+\\infty}\\frac{\\ln(2x)}{1+\\ln x}$ يساوي: (أ) $\\ln2$، (ب) $1$، (ج) $2$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q4_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (ب)، إذ $\\displaystyle\\frac{\\ln(2x)}{1+\\ln x}=\\frac{\\frac{\\ln2}{\\ln x}+1}{\\frac1{\\ln x}+1}$ ومنه النهاية تساوي $1$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e2_q4_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s1_e3",
          "nodeType": "EXERCISE",
