              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "2.25 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s1_e4_q5",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s1_e4",
          "orderIndex": 5,
          "label": "السؤال 5",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s1_e4_q5_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أ) اثبت أن الدالة $H:x\\mapsto\\frac{-3-2\\ln x}{x}$ دالة أصلية للدالة $h:x\\mapsto\\frac{1+2\\ln x}{x^2}$ على المجال $]0;+\\infty[$. ب) استنتج مساحة الحيز المستوي المحدد بـ$(C_f)$ و$(\\Delta)$ والمستقيمين $x=1$ و$x=e$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e4_q5_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$H'(x)=h(x)$ على $]0;+\\infty[$. ومنه $\\displaystyle\\int_1^e\\frac{1+2\\ln x}{x^2}\\,dx=[H(x)]_1^e=3-\\frac5e$، وبالتالي $\\mathcal{A}=(3-\\frac5e)\\,u.a$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s1_e4_q5_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
