          "maxPoints": 4,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "عين الاقتراح الصحيح الوحيد من بين الاقتراحات الثلاثة في كل حالة من الحالات الآتية دون التبرير."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e1_q1",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e1",
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "label": "السؤال 1",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الدالة $f$ المعرفة على $\\mathbb{R}$ بـ $f(x)=8x^3+1$. الدالة الأصلية $F$ للدالة $f$ والتي تنعدم عند $1$ هي: (أ) $F(x)=x^4+x-2$، (ب) $F(x)=2x^4+x-3$، (ج) $F(x)=2x^4-2x$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q1_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (ب)."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q1_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة، والتبرير غير مطلوب."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e1_q2",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e1",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "السؤال 2",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الدالة $g$ المعرفة على $\\mathbb{R}$ بـ $g(x)=\\frac{e^x}{1+e^x}$. القيمة المتوسطة للدالة $g$ على المجال $[-\\ln2;\\ln2]$ هي: (أ) $2\\ln2$، (ب) $\\frac1{2\\ln2}$، (ج) $\\frac12$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q2_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (ج)."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة، والتبرير غير مطلوب."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e1_q3",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e1",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "السؤال 3",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "حل المعادلة $\\ln(x-2)+\\ln(x-4)=3\\ln2$ على المجال $]4;+\\infty[$ هو: (أ) $6$، (ب) $8$، (ج) $9$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q3_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (أ)."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q3_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة، والتبرير غير مطلوب."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e1_q4",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e1",
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "label": "السؤال 4",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q4_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الدالة $h$ المعرفة على $]-1;1[$ بـ $h(x)=\\ln\\left(\\frac{1+x}{1-x}\\right)$ هي: (أ) زوجية، (ب) فردية، (ج) لا زوجية ولا فردية."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q4_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "الإجابة الصحيحة هي (ب)."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e1_q4_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة، والتبرير غير مطلوب."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e2",
          "nodeType": "EXERCISE",
          "parentId": null,
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "التمرين الثاني",
          "maxPoints": 4,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$P(X)=(2X-1)(X^2+X-2)$ كثيرة حدود معرفة على $\\mathbb{R}$."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e2_q1",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e2",
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "label": "السؤال 1",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "ادرس إشارة $P(X)$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q1_solution_table",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "image",
              "value": "جدول إشارة $P(X)$.",
              "assetId": "s2_e2_sign_table"
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q1_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$P(X)$ سالب تماما على $]-\\infty;-2[$ و$]\\frac12;1[$، وموجب تماما على $]-2;\\frac12[$ و$]1;+\\infty[$، وينعدم عند $-2$ و$\\frac12$ و$1$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q1_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e2_q2",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e2",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "السؤال 2",
          "maxPoints": 2,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أ) حل في المجال $]0;+\\infty[$ المعادلة $(2\\ln x-1)((\\ln x)^2+\\ln x-2)=0$. ب) استنتج في $]0;+\\infty[$ حلول المتراجحة $(2\\ln x-1)((\\ln x)^2+\\ln x-2)<0$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q2_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "مجموعة حلول المعادلة هي $\\{e^{-2};\\sqrt e;e\\}$. ومجموعة حلول المتراجحة هي $]0;e^{-2}[\\cup]\\sqrt e;e[$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "2 نقطتان."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e2_q3",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e2",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "السؤال 3",
          "maxPoints": 1,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "حل في المجال $]-1;+\\infty[$ المعادلة $(\\ln(x+1))^2+\\ln(x+1)-2=0$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q3_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "مجموعة الحلول هي $\\{e^{-2}-1;e-1\\}$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e2_q3_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3",
          "nodeType": "EXERCISE",
          "parentId": null,
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "label": "التمرين الثالث",
          "maxPoints": 4,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "المتتالية العددية $(u_n)$ معرفة بـ: $u_0=4$، ومن أجل كل عدد طبيعي $n$: $u_{n+1}=\\frac34u_n-\\frac12$."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_q1",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3",
          "orderIndex": 1,
          "label": "السؤال 1",
          "maxPoints": 0.5,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q1_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "احسب $u_1$ و$u_2$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q1_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$u_1=\\frac52$ و$u_2=\\frac{11}{8}$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q1_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "0.5 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_q2",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": "السؤال 2",
          "maxPoints": 1.5,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q2_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "أ) برهن بالتراجع أنه من أجل كل عدد طبيعي $n$: $u_n>-2$. ب) بين أن المتتالية $(u_n)$ متناقصة تماما."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q2_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "بالبرهان بالتراجع نحصل على $u_n>-2$ لكل $n\\in\\mathbb{N}$. كما أن $u_{n+1}-u_n=-\\frac14(u_n+2)$، ومنه $(u_n)$ متناقصة تماما."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q2_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1.5 نقطة حسب سلم التصحيح."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_q3",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3",
          "orderIndex": 3,
          "label": "السؤال 3",
          "maxPoints": 1.5,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q3_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "المتتالية العددية $(v_n)$ المعرفة على $\\mathbb{N}$ بـ: $v_n=u_n+2$. أ) بين أن $(v_n)$ متتالية هندسية أساسها $\\frac34$. ب) اكتب $v_n$ بدلالة $n$ ثم بين أن $u_n=6(\\frac34)^n-2$. ج) احسب $\\lim_{n\\to+\\infty}u_n$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q3_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$v_{n+1}=\\frac34v_n$، ومنه أساسها $q=\\frac34$. وبما أن $v_0=6$ فإن $v_n=6(\\frac34)^n$، وبالتالي $u_n=6(\\frac34)^n-2$. إذن $\\lim_{n\\to+\\infty}u_n=-2$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q3_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1.5 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e3_q4",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_e3",
          "orderIndex": 4,
          "label": "السؤال 4",
          "maxPoints": 0.5,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q4_prompt",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "احسب كلا من $S_n=v_0+v_1+\\cdots+v_n$ و$T_n=\\frac1{2+u_0}+\\frac1{2+u_1}+\\cdots+\\frac1{2+u_n}$ بدلالة $n$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q4_solution",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "$S_n=24\\left(1-(\\frac34)^{n+1}\\right)$ و$T_n=\\frac12\\left((\\frac43)^{n+1}-1\\right)$."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_e3_q4_rubric",
              "role": "RUBRIC",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "0.5 نقطة."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s2_e4",
          "nodeType": "EXERCISE",
          "parentId": null,
          "orderIndex": 5,
          "label": "التمرين الرابع",
